My modifications to the standard android AlarmClock.
Changed under the APACHE 2.0 license.

* Name Alarms
* Extra alarm settings:
    * vibrate only            (no ringtone, only vibrate)
    * alarm volume            (max vol % to play alarm at [1-100])
??    * alarm volume increase   (seconds to increase from 10% [1-60])
    * alarm duration          (minutes to auto-turn off [1-60]) 
??    * tone delay              (ms pause between ringtone plays [100-10000])
    * snooze duration         (number of minutes to snooze [1-60])

Planned Features:
  * Disable alarms during calls
